:auto; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; padding:0px; text-rendering:geometricprecision; text-size-adjust:100%; vertical-align:baseline; width:960px\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:baseline\">Chiếc Bentley Mulsanne EWB của đại gia này thuộc đời 2018. Mulsanne EWB không quá hiếm tại Việt Nam nhưng sedan siêu sang này gây chú ý bởi ngoại thất 2 tone màu xám ghi và vàng cát sang trọng.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"banner size_masthead\" data-darkreader-inline-bgimage=\"\" data-darkreader-inline-border-bottom=\"\" data-darkreader-inline-border-left=\"\" data-darkreader-inline-border-right=\"\" data-darkreader-inline-border-top=\"\" data-darkreader-inline-color=\"\" data-darkreader-inline-outline=\"\" id=\"advMiddle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-rendering: geometricprecision; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-left: 60px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 17.6px; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: 100%; overflow: visible; color: rgb(209, 206, 199); position: relative; float: none; clear: both; left: -250px; font-family: &quot;Noto Serif&quot;, serif; text-align: justify; --darkreader-inline-border-top: initial; --darkreader-inline-border-right: initial; --darkreader-inline-border-bottom: initial; --darkreader-inline-border-left: initial; --darkreader-inline-outline: initial; --darkreader-inline-color:#d1cec7; --darkreader-inline-bgimage:none; margin-top: 60px !important; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 60px !important; background-image: none !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; width: 1100px !important; height: auto !important;\">\r\n<div class=\"z2-zads-zone\" data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor=\"\" data-darkreader-inline-